{"tid":984944,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"到底啲領養撚諗咩","createTime":"2019-01-17T08:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T10:43:50.000Z","uid":200788,"like":101,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e1989045abbfabc00d014077f7252c9bf2a3d3ca","tid":984944,"uid":200788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWmFGPk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWmFGPk.png&h=200f80d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要家訪都算 仲要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你</span>得閒可以見下佢？<br />\n你咁同擺隻狗喺人地屋企養有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時你得閒人地唔得閒咁點？<br />\n想見隻狗就自己養啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身真係想領養 但領養個班人到底有冇設身處地？<br />\n家訪其實我都覺戇鳩 如果真係有養過狗就知 好多時你唔喺屋企/冇人陪佢玩 佢都只係搵個位攤 最緊要冇雜物 日日帶佢散步 不過家訪好似已經係必經之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲自己屋企養緊兩隻狗 然後質疑我本身有隻狗 養多隻係咪真係得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d21dc08fcaa179c24dce7607160f1b4dba0289","tid":984944,"uid":107927,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:16:41.000Z","msg":"擺明自己唔想養想叫其他人養"},{"pid":"4e7479f1f584b417d087659323ee326069228ef2","tid":984944,"uid":65470,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:19:01.000Z","msg":"比D 領養撚 撚完兩次<br />\n我以為只買不領養 DKLM"},{"pid":"c62db87e0552cdc45bd0bb4bbfe0ff94a6bb3073","tid":984944,"uid":65470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比D 領養撚 撚完兩次<br />\n我以<span style=\"color: red;\">後</span>只買不領養 DKLM</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cebbd1cfa5492f8a341fb657fe2efa585e105ce4","tid":984944,"uid":63515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"大部份都好主觀又自私"},{"pid":"4383ad3276e0dd9699204eebce0c001ae81cc41d","tid":984944,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep